Lost in the hospital in unclear conditions, in the mists of the 90’s, when she had only two months of life, little girl, sickly and helpless, and then adopted by a wealthy family from Italy, in the same years when the adoption was vaguely regulated, a young woman from Iasi, now a blonde and beautiful girl, met again in Iasi with her parents.
