Constantin Brâncuși, the peasant god.
Rockefeller: "How can I help you?"
Brancusi: "Take the workshop too!"
The great sculptor had a big dream: to be someone, to become famous, to hear about him all over the world.
Behind his fame, however, something almost forgotten today is hidden, when millions of success stories are delivered to us, recipes for success in life.
